==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Glaum
<hw>Glaum</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <ety>[Etymol.
uncertain.]</ety> <def>To grope with the hands, as in the dark.</def>
<mark>[Scot.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>To glaum at</b></col>, <cd>to grasp or snatch at; to
aspire to.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Wha <qex>glaum'd at</qex> kingdoms three.</q>
<rj><qau>Burns.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Glave</ent>⟦br⟧
